response.overview: An ambitious young executive is sent to retrieve his company's CEO from an idyllic but mysterious "wellness center" at a remote location in the Swiss Alps but soon suspects that the spa's miraculous treatments are not what they seem.
response.tagline: All of us are human. None of us are immune.
response.title: A Cure for Wellness
